headline: DOJ probes Netflix’s power over filmmakers in Warner deal review
summary: The department is seeking to determine whether the deal “may substantially lessen competition or tend to create a monopoly in violation of Section 7 of the Clayton Act or Section 2 of the Sherman Act"

headline: Steve Jobs Was Notoriously Demanding But Pixar's Ed Catmull Never Had A Loud Disagreement With The Apple Co-Founder: This Is His Secret

headline: Under mounting toy pressures, Hasbro has a secret sauce that Mattel hasn't matched
